{"tid":1737800,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[可能old news]發現尖咀狗窿 便衣狗出入","createTime":"2019-11-19T05:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T19:35:35.000Z","uid":41237,"like":96,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"c3800223c96eb69191cc7099e3945d199c6950b5","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/46hJG7J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F46hJG7J.jpg&h=d48a79ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VqpjZUC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVqpjZUC.jpg&h=4ac5090c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一開始係為咗避佐敦大街嘅tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走咗入柯士甸道，尖沙咀警署後門<br />\n點知發現半小時內，至少五個便衣從大閘出入<br />\n咁梗係即刻影相啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/19/125730_ae4b7f8225a23e859ddee6129b282ead.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F19%2F125730_ae4b7f8225a23e859ddee6129b282ead.jpeg&h=ec6a9fb6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/19/125809_746b8855cc9a657618fceb4934518bda.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F19%2F125809_746b8855cc9a657618fceb4934518bda.jpeg&h=0bb9275c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/19/125842_68549d4b6fb458a1620fade644e42e95.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F19%2F125842_68549d4b6fb458a1620fade644e42e95.jpeg&h=a693d770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n估唔到連圍裙阿叔都有，頭耷耷出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我舉機仲令到幾個便衣寧願匿返入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好快，佢哋居然舉黑旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰度附近冇手足、冇記者<br />\n仲針對我一個人嘅特徵，嗌咪驅散<br />\n我就知道捉住咗佢哋春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最終45分鐘以上黑旗，冇射過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三次派出綠曱甴出閘嚇走人<br />\n都唔成功，仲越來越多手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171d49e1050b45175243beca7f673849f14ed315","tid":1737800,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:04:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入-----&gt; <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=071e669e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"c23bf2002dea5bb45961c18b1c8220fd21ccc1f2","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> wow咗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />old news is so唔識串<br />\n(但又冇人喺嗰度做哨喎)"},{"pid":"b73da0a4065ae7479862262af9b7918a723b692f","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:07:31.000Z","msg":"我又冇撚狗，街坊look<br />\n班狗嗌咪30次以上嗌我走<br />\n慶過火屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7b8fdecfcd30449b62f923345f5bb639856a6b","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:08:49.000Z","msg":"黑旗喺大閘右上方<br />\n大家可以放大黎睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上如有半點虛言，我死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b46d6a563611ac66c9b19a98de7b7cf3636028","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:09:08.000Z","msg":"自推十連 1"},{"pid":"9283d96ca8759e25bcd1daae4e4150dc37cfffcf","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:09:30.000Z","msg":"自推十連 2"},{"pid":"380cee39b30159f57938644d2d479515bdf06431","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:09:41.000Z","msg":"自推十連 3"},{"pid":"c3a311b7d33eb2b60718c666d88be5adb7471e8d","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:10:44.000Z","msg":"自推十連 4<br />\n大家最近希望玩多啲油尖旺九龍<br />\n棄港島 我覺得呢個資訊大家都需要知"},{"pid":"bbc8a8cc0bcfaf9cb5c58bc83b9a40fcb2a3bd1d","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:11:10.000Z","msg":"自推十連 5"},{"pid":"c8153c1665d3f03aa4c4a337480b5a4b8aead0d9","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:11:21.000Z","msg":"自推十連 6"},{"pid":"a3a7feb696f635219ddc66204a18513dd89dca05","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:11:50.000Z","msg":"自推十連 7"},{"pid":"8fa60b87b18ca2e370d34364947f2040850476a4","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"自推十連 8<br />\n有冇人俾啲意見幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82421b60e2270c2bbe8a9f41d68dd95e528b5284","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:12:56.000Z","msg":"自推十連 9"},{"pid":"d15c72f6c0cbb6b611e8f33e01f34f309bc56604","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:13:18.000Z","msg":"自推十連 10<br />\n樓主真可憐，自己說自己笑.jpg"},{"pid":"925922dcaa91e470c750bba55c372bac81a5b4c9","tid":1737800,"uid":8439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:13:35.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"8e89437bb8ba23d1b74107dd3d90ca0513a75d29","tid":1737800,"uid":19501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:17:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca952e9c911bb929a5bbdd91fb7b443c017c7092","tid":1737800,"uid":195812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"街坊裝幾時都可以撚狗"},{"pid":"ceec32461f7c71e37704c3cd53a06c6f9edd9001","tid":1737800,"uid":8657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />走"},{"pid":"ed12de3c46ed386f86f28f83d35571539f14067e","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:22:33.000Z","msg":"補充：呢度即係佐敦站彌敦道行入一條街<br />\n軍記前少少，好多地產鋪嗰度<br />\n尋日係彌敦道柯士甸道交界十字路口開戰<br />\n冇乜手足入過嚟，我叫過兩個記者留低<br />\n話pooppoop對冇示威者嘅地方扯旗<br />\n<br />\n記者表示：唔留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc10508f87d4d1767e18a94dc053756978d2e55","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:26:09.000Z","msg":"「柯士甸道上面嘅市民立即離開！」<br />\n「你哋正參與緊一場非法集結！」<br />\n「請你地立即離開！」<br />\n「否則警方將使用催淚煙進行驅散！」<br />\n「_色衫、_色褲，我哋影低晒你㗎啦！」<br />\n「請你地立即離開！」x1000<br />\n<br />\n阿sir，我好悶呀，仲有冇下一句啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扯旗咁耐，捨唔捨得出啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d49cc6ab34f0eec2c9c97301f0113917f717800","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:28:17.000Z","msg":"Mon po狗你好<br />\n尋日你嗌咁多次我都詐聽唔到<br />\n係咪好嬲呢？有冇喉嚨痛啊？<br />\n都話你拉我唔到㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錄影？你錄到啲咩啊？錄到我東張西望？"},{"pid":"6be3012aaae56ce1dc6caba125cfad5fe47dd46c","tid":1737800,"uid":248571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:30:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ae06522917a8ab4764fbc043db646d4954d70b5","tid":1737800,"uid":65381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:31:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9425d63e1bbecd6e03a837890622b82bc479e7e","tid":1737800,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:33:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75f351d4c8e368a5b8654d025b9a9b63455d2ae9","tid":1737800,"uid":47593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:03:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"117d666d8d927291d6f593ae499a3fe96eaf9202","tid":1737800,"uid":303054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:04:36.000Z","msg":"推唔到都照推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db997985198f5541ebbfbf726953e2dc7cf9c538","tid":1737800,"uid":190730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:07:35.000Z","msg":"Tsui"},{"pid":"e23bf6fac1c8966b4b1917491bc9177490159ad5","tid":1737800,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:08:18.000Z","msg":"18-8-2019 (原片）香港警察踩示威者頭部<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0975721830d358e224689fcf614d8110258a69ec","tid":1737800,"uid":192722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019