d/2019/11/19/125809_746b8855cc9a657618fceb4934518bda.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F19%2F125809_746b8855cc9a657618fceb4934518bda.jpeg&h=0bb9275c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/19/125842_68549d4b6fb458a1620fade644e42e95.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F19%2F125842_68549d4b6fb458a1620fade644e42e95.jpeg&h=a693d770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n估唔到連圍裙阿叔都有，頭耷耷出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我舉機仲令到幾個便衣寧願匿返入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好快，佢哋居然舉黑旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰度附近冇手足、冇記者<br />\n仲針對我一個人嘅特徵，嗌咪驅散<br />\n我就知道捉住咗佢哋春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最終45分鐘以上黑旗，冇射過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三次派出綠曱甴出閘嚇走人<br />\n都唔成功，仲越來越多手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"11f26ac804a60d7d06cbf747686296c4c93188f6","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcf80a04cd809e3b0c4b3b604874043d16ed85fc","tid":1737800,"uid":282490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b73da0a4065ae7479862262af9b7918a723b692f","tid":1737800,"uid":41237,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:07:31.000Z","msg":"我又冇撚狗，街坊look<br />\n班狗嗌咪30次以上嗌我走<br />\n慶過火屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br 